t\t\t<span class=\"entry_duration mpfe_fix_lh\"><\/span>\t\t\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"song_buy_icons compact_buy_icons transition3 clearfix mobile_visibility_hide\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8305349 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8305349\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-1\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Introduction<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8820442 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8820442\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Choosing the right enterprise software can make or break your operations. Salesforce and ServiceNow are two of the biggest names in the market, but they serve very different needs.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce CRM holds over 22% of the global CRM market, according to <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.statista.com\/topics\/8218\/salesforcecom\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Statista\u2019s report<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. It powers customer relationships for over 150,000 businesses worldwide, including major brands such as Amazon, Toyota, and Unilever.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ServiceNow, on the other hand, dominates the IT service management (ITSM) space. As of 2024, it controls nearly 40% of the ITSM market, supporting over 7,700 enterprise customers, with many in finance, healthcare, and government.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So which one is right for you?<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This guide breaks down the core strengths of both platforms, compares features, use cases, and costs, and helps you decide which tool is better suited to your business challenges, whether it\u2019s managing customers or streamlining internal systems.<\/span><\/p><p><b>Key Takeaways<\/b><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce leads in CRM, sales automation, and customer engagement.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ServiceNow excels at IT service management and internal workflow automation.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce offers vast third-party integrations via AppExchange.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ServiceNow provides strong backend process automation across departments.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Choosing the right tool depends on your team\u2019s biggest pain point.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0c0f628 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0c0f628\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-2\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Platform Overview: What They Are and What They Do Best<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7898f76 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7898f76\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce partners are companies trained and approved by Salesforce to help businesses use its tools. These partners know how to set up, change, and manage the system. They help with planning, building, and improving how Salesforce works for your team.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">There are two main types:<\/span><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Implementation partners<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> help install and customize the platform.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Consulting partners<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> guide your strategy and help you get more from your data.<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Some companies do both. They can build your system and teach your team how to use it well. These experts can save you time, money, and stress.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-30c3ebd all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"30c3ebd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-3\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Why Your Business Needs a Salesforce Partner<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e0162fc all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e0162fc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Salesforce CRM: Built for Customer-Facing Teams<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c0d5464 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c0d5464\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/salesforce\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is the world\u2019s most widely used customer relationship management (CRM) platform. Its core strength lies in helping sales, marketing, and support teams track customer interactions, automate outreach, and close deals faster.<\/span><\/p><p><strong>Companies use Salesforce to:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manage sales pipelines<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Run email marketing campaigns<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Track customer service cases<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Analyze customer behavior and trends<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It\u2019s trusted by organizations of all sizes, from startups to Fortune 500 companies. Brands that want to strengthen customer relationships, boost conversions, and improve team productivity often choose Salesforce Implementation Services.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1591723 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1591723\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/What-They-Are-and-What-They-Do-Best.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-23943\" alt=\"What They Are and What They Do Best\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/What-They-Are-and-What-They-Do-Best.webp 1280w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/What-They-Are-and-What-They-Do-Best-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/What-They-Are-and-What-They-Do-Best-1024x576.webp 1024w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/What-They-Are-and-What-They-Do-Best-768x432.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-285d38c all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"285d38c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-4\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">ServiceNow: Built for Internal Operations and IT<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-44a5d8d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"44a5d8d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ServiceNow specializes in IT Service Management (ITSM). It helps companies manage incidents, automate workflows, and run internal operations more efficiently.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While it originated in IT, ServiceNow has expanded into HR, finance, legal, and field service operations, providing teams with a single platform to automate repetitive tasks and streamline approvals.<\/span><\/p><p><strong>Businesses use ServiceNow Implementation Services to:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manage IT help desk requests<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Monitor service outages and incidents<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Automate HR onboarding and offboarding<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Track facility maintenance requests<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ServiceNow is ideal for large organizations with complex internal systems, especially those looking to replace manual processes with structured, automated workflows.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a6001ce all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a6001ce\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Core Features Comparison Salesforce vs ServiceNow<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cdcb627 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"cdcb627\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<table><tbody><tr><td><p><b>Feature<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><b>Salesforce<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><b>ServiceNow<\/b><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>CRM Capabilities<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Industry-leading CRM with advanced tools for sales, service, and marketing.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Basic CRM functionality; not its core strength.<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>ITSM Capabilities<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Limited IT support tools; mainly focused on external customer management.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Core strength. Manages IT tickets, incidents, and service catalogs.<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Workflow Automation<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Strong automation with Flow Builder and Process Builder tools.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Powerful automation engine across IT, HR, legal, and facilities workflows.<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Customizability<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Highly customizable through AppExchange and custom coding (Apex).<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Also highly customizable using low-code\/no-code tools within the platform.<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>User Interface<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Modern, intuitive dashboard with AI-powered insights and drag-and-drop tools.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Clean interface tailored for process-driven tasks; less visual customization.<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Mobile Support<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce mobile app supports full CRM access on the go.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mobile access is available; best for approvals and ticket updates.<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cac9908 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"cac9908\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-5\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Integration Capabilities and Ecosystems<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a682466 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a682466\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Salesforce Integration: Built to Connect Everything<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0ddcf76 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0ddcf76\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce is known for its powerful integration capabilities. It connects with over 3,000 third-party apps via the Salesforce AppExchange, the largest B2B app marketplace in the world. From email marketing tools like Mailchimp to ERP systems like SAP and Oracle, Salesforce can plug into nearly every major business system.<\/span><\/p><p><strong>Salesforce also supports:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Custom APIs for internal apps.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Native integrations with Google Workspace, Microsoft 365, Slack, and more.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Middleware platforms like MuleSoft (which Salesforce owns) for complex data sync across systems.<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For businesses that rely on multiple tools, Salesforce CRM ensures smooth communication between departments, improving data flow and team collaboration.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-64fdbdd all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"64fdbdd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">ServiceNow Integration: Optimized for IT Workflows<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3465105 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3465105\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ServiceNow also integrates well, particularly with IT, HR, and security tools. Its IntegrationHub allows teams to connect systems like Microsoft Azure, Workday, Jira, and cybersecurity platforms. It supports both out-of-the-box connectors and custom workflows using low-code design.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ServiceNow excels at syncing backend systems that manage tickets, approvals, and operational tasks. It reduces manual handoffs by creating automated end-to-end service workflows.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-28f20ef all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"28f20ef\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Salesforce vs ServiceNow Integration: Best of Both Worlds<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-707be59 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"707be59\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Many enterprises use both platforms together, Salesforce for managing customer-facing processes, and ServiceNow for handling internal services.<\/span><\/p><p><strong>For example:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A sales team logs a service request in Salesforce, and it auto-creates a ticket in ServiceNow.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">IT support teams using ServiceNow can view customer history pulled from Salesforce during issue resolution.<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This type of integration helps break down silos between departments and improves response times.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-25f9725 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"25f9725\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">AppExchange vs App Engine: Ecosystem Strength<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-13b4aa9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"13b4aa9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>The Salesforce AppExchange<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> offers a vast selection of pre-built solutions, covering industries such as finance, healthcare, and retail. It\u2019s designed to extend CRM functionality without heavy development.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>ServiceNow App Engine<\/b><span> focuses more on custom internal applications. It&#8217;s designed for process automation within departments such as IT, HR, and legal.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-59a8ecd all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"59a8ecd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Real-World Use Case:<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4583138 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4583138\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A global bank utilizes Salesforce Services in San Francisco to monitor client interactions and manage the sales of financial products. When a customer raises a technical issue, the request is logged, tracked, and resolved in ServiceNow by the IT team. The data is synced back to Salesforce, so relationship managers stay informed without switching systems.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b83f760 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"b83f760\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Salesforce-AppExchange-vs-ServiceNow-App-Engine.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-23944\" alt=\"Salesforce AppExchange vs ServiceNow App Engine\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Salesforce-AppExchange-vs-ServiceNow-App-Engine.webp 1280w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Salesforce-AppExchange-vs-ServiceNow-App-Engine-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Salesforce-AppExchange-vs-ServiceNow-App-Engine-1024x576.webp 1024w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Salesforce-AppExchange-vs-ServiceNow-App-Engine-768x432.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c4c6211 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c4c6211\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Industry Use Cases: Who Wins Where?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-249c3dc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"249c3dc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce and ServiceNow serve different parts of the enterprise. Knowing where each one excels helps businesses avoid costly mismatches and get faster returns on investment.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-670a105 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"670a105\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-5\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Where Salesforce Dominates<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-40acf2d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"40acf2d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce is purpose-built for customer-facing teams. Its tools are designed to help businesses attract, engage, and retain customers.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b366bc6 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b366bc6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Key Use Cases:<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-401fb92 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"401fb92\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Sales Automation: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sales teams use Salesforce to manage leads, track opportunities, and forecast revenue. It streamlines the sales cycle and provides real-time visibility into pipeline performance.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Marketing Workflows:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> With tools like Marketing Cloud and Pardot, companies can run targeted campaigns, track engagement, and personalize customer journeys at scale.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Customer Service &amp; Support:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Salesforce Service Cloud helps support teams manage cases, respond to inquiries, and deliver faster resolutions, whether by phone, chat, or email.<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><b>Best Fit: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Retail, e-commerce, finance, telecom, SaaS companies\u2014any business where revenue depends on strong customer relationships.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-39353a9 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"39353a9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Where ServiceNow Services Excels<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9f1d478 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9f1d478\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ServiceNow is built for internal operations and service management. It helps departments run smoothly behind the scenes, automating routine work and reducing delays.<\/span><\/p><p><b>Key Use Cases:<\/b><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>IT Operations and Incident Management:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> ServiceNow ITSM allows teams to track outages, manage help desk tickets, and enforce SLAs. It\u2019s essential for companies with large or complex IT environments.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Internal Workflow Automation: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From procurement to legal request approvals, ServiceNow connects cross-departmental processes and automates manual handoffs, streamlining workflows.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>HR and Facilities Management: <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">HR teams use it for onboarding, leave requests, and employee lifecycle tasks. Facilities teams can manage maintenance requests and asset tracking in one place.<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><b>Best Fit:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Healthcare, manufacturing, education, logistics, government agencies\u2014organizations that need strong operational support behind the scenes.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-59685d9 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"59685d9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-6\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Pricing and Scalability<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d2043da elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d2043da\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce offers flexible plans starting at $25\/user\/month for small businesses. For advanced needs, pricing climbs to $165 for the Enterprise plan and $330 for Unlimited. The top-tier Einstein 1 Sales plan runs $500\/user\/month, adding AI tools and deep sales engagement features.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ServiceNow it services management doesn\u2019t list public pricing. Estimates suggest starting costs around $100\/user\/month, but actual rates depend on the number of modules and users. Businesses are encouraged to request a custom quote.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Both platforms scale easily with growing teams, but Salesforce is better suited for customer-facing teams, while ServiceNow scales well for internal service operations.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a50ae40 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"a50ae40\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1280\" height=\"720\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Salesforce-vs-servicenow-Pricing-and-Scalability.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-23945\" alt=\"Salesforce vs servicenow Pricing and Scalability\" srcset=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Salesforce-vs-servicenow-Pricing-and-Scalability.webp 1280w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Salesforce-vs-servicenow-Pricing-and-Scalability-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Salesforce-vs-servicenow-Pricing-and-Scalability-1024x576.webp 1024w, https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/Salesforce-vs-servicenow-Pricing-and-Scalability-768x432.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8830b2f all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8830b2f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Pros and Cons<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d22b1a6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d22b1a6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Start by writing down what your business needs. What do you want Salesforce to do? Do you need help with setup, training, or support? What problems are you trying to fix? When you know your goals, it\u2019s easier to find a partner who can meet them.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f8ac3a8 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f8ac3a8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Salesforce CRM<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2034580 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2034580\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Pros:<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d967368 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d967368\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Industry-leading CRM with powerful sales and marketing tools.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Highly customizable with vast third-party app support.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Scales easily across departments and regions.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Strong data analytics and reporting features.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fast ROI for customer-facing teams.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aa53042 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"aa53042\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Cons:<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7665033 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7665033\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Steep learning curve for new users.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Can become expensive at higher tiers.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Requires skilled admins or developers for complex setups.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Integration with legacy systems may need third-party tools.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-66aef7f all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"66aef7f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">ServiceNow<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c778315 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c778315\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Pros:<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-df7a9b7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"df7a9b7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Best-in-class for IT service management and internal workflows.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Strong automation and low-code capabilities.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Centralized platform for multiple departments (IT, HR, Legal).<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">High impact on operational efficiency and ticket resolution times.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0fa7dbf all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0fa7dbf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Cons:<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c614331 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c614331\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pricing is not transparent and may vary widely.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Less suitable for external customer engagement.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Setup and customization often require IT involvement.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Time-to-value can be slower for smaller teams or non-IT use cases.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9f81b99 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"9f81b99\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Choosing the Right Tool for Your Business Pain<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bc8a906 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"bc8a906\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>What\u2019s your biggest headache right now?<\/b><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Are leads slipping through the cracks?<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Is your sales team struggling to track deals?<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Are your support agents juggling too many disconnected systems?<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If so, Salesforce is the tool to bring structure, visibility, and speed to your customer engagement.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">But if your problems are behind the scenes:<\/span><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">IT tickets piling up<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manual approval delays<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Disconnected internal workflows<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Then, ServiceNow is the platform built to solve those bottlenecks.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-635973e all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"635973e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-7\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Quick Decision Checklist:<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-58b7ded elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"58b7ded\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<table><tbody><tr><td><p><b>Your Need<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><b>Best Fit<\/b><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sales tracking and forecasting<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Marketing campaign automation<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Customer support and case management<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">IT service desk and ticketing<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ServiceNow<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">HR onboarding and internal requests<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ServiceNow<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cross-department workflow automation<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">ServiceNow<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-227499f all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"227499f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-8\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Hybrid Approach:<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-672d6e5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"672d6e5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Some enterprises get the best of both worlds by integrating Salesforce vs ServiceNow. For example, Salesforce CRM handles customer-facing activities, while ServiceNow manages internal service delivery. This setup seamlessly connects front-end actions to back-end responses.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ab88dec all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ab88dec\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-9\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">How Can Mountainise Help?<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d3e8be2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d3e8be2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mountainise works closely with businesses to solve real problems using Salesforce and ServiceNow. If you need help setting up Salesforce, connecting it to your tools, or making sure your ServiceNow workflows run smoothly, we\u2019ve got you covered.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here\u2019s what we do:<\/span><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Set up custom Salesforce integrations that fit your team\u2019s needs.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/><br \/><\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Build and automate workflows inside ServiceNow.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/><br \/><\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Connect Salesforce and ServiceNow so your teams don\u2019t work in silos.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><br \/><br \/><\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Offer hands-on support to keep things running without delays.<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Want smoother systems and faster results? <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/book-a-free-session\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Book a free session now<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-801c624 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"801c624\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">The Final Verdict<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1c4d2a2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1c4d2a2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If your focus is customer relationships, sales growth, or marketing automation, Salesforce is the clear winner. However, if your biggest challenges involve IT service delivery, internal workflows, or operational efficiency, ServiceNow is designed for that purpose.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Choosing the right platform depends on what\u2019s slowing your business down: external engagement or internal operations.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Need both? Integration is possible and powerful.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Need help with Salesforce 